      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Seriously, this beauty is in stunning, showroom-ready condition! It\u2019s been kept in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. If you're looking for something that feels and looks brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely it. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin!",
