    {
      "id": "sybil_25_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_25",
      "description": "Offering a concourse-level BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies. This specimen exhibits zero subframe fatigue and has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement with documented tolerances. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M-differential for optimal torque vectoring. Finished in Titanium Silver over Nappa leather, the chassis maintains factory rigidity with original bushings and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key enthusiast investment with a comprehensive service history and no deferred maintenance.",
