    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Every panel is original, and the factory alloy wheels are pristine, devoid of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and all interior surfaces retain their original matte finish and crisp, factory feel. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder containing every service record since its delivery. The engine bay is detailed to perfection, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the buyer seeking the absolute finest example available that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, this is the one.",
